end

on removeSprites me
  [  0] getprop 116 ............................. <pSprite>
  [  2] pusharglist 1 ........................... <pSprite>
  [  4] extcall 75 .............................. <ilk(pSprite)>
  [  6] pushsymb 76 ............................. <#sprite>
  [  8] nteq .................................... <ilk(pSprite) <> #sprite>
  [  9] jmpifz [ 17] ............................ if ilk(pSprite) <> #sprite then
